snippet.title: Cloudy Super Mario Bros. U - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Cloudy SMBU is (probably) going to be the first complete New Super Mario Bros U hack/mod, released to the Public!
This hack will contain:
-24+ New Stages
-New and returning Mario music
-Tons of new tilesets/level themes
-A few retextured enemies/objects

It will (most likely) release around early November, so look forward to more info!
